Paper: hep-th/0304071

Date: 2003-04-08

Title: Near-Horizon States of Black Holes and Calogero Models

Authors: B Basu-Mallick, Pijush K. Ghosh and Kumar S. Gupta

Comments: 3 pages, talk given at PASCOS03, TIFR, Mumbai

We find self-adjoint extensions of the rational Calogero model in presence ofthe harmonic interaction. The corresponding eigenfunctions may describe thenear-horizon quantum states of certain types of black holes.